pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `352b5d3` to `3f2da47`
pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `352b5d3` to `3f2da47`.
Commits
  • 3f2da47 Pull latest SPHINCS from PQClean; bump liboqs version to 0.6.0-dev (#950)
  • e82b58a Patch Kyber, Dilithium, and SPHINCS to use our SHA3 (#948)
  • eccb24f Fix OQS_PORTABLE_BUILD logic for upstream imports (#941)
  • 7dc4b37 Refactor SHA3 implementations and improve API (#922)
  • See full diff in compare view
